RELATIONS; FOOD INDUSTRY -- CONTRACTS; UNITED FOOD AND COMMERCIAL WORKERS 
INTERNATIONAL UNION; FOOD INDUSTRY -- WAGES AND SALARIES; PART TIME EMPLOYMENT; 
EMPLOYEE BENEFITS; HEALTH INSURANCE -- ELIGIBILITY; PENSIONS 
</P>
