ORANGE; HEALTH HAZARDS; HERBICIDES; MEDICAL RESEARCH; HAZARDOUS MATERIALS; 
VIETNAM WAR VETERANS -- HEALTH; LIABILITY; VICTIM COMPENSATION; CENTERS FOR 
DISEASE CONTROL 
</P>
