Pacific Bank branch in Fullerton and escaped in a car driven by a second man. 
2. Police arrested one suspect, but the other managed to drive off in the 
getaway car. He eventually was cornered by a police dog behind a house in 
Anaheim after wrecking the vehicle. 
</P>
