<P>
Photo, Less is more at the Palos Verdes Art Center's Beckstrand Gallery, where 
Wendy Katz views one of Seiji Kunishima's stone sculptures in a show titled 
"Zero Plus One." Also on view, from 1 to 4 p.m. Monday through Saturday, are 
graphite-on-paper drawings by Mari Omori. The show's title alludes to the 
minimalist nature of both artists' creations. HARRY CHASE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
