<TEXT>
<P>
Chrysler Delays New Luxury Car: Chrysler Corp. disclosed that it will 
indefinitely delay the development of its LX luxury car program. The company 
instead will develop a mid-size car to replace the Dodge Spirit and Plymouth 
Acclaim around 1994. 
</P>
