<TEXT>
<P>
Salomon to Cut Back Philipp Bros. Unit: The parent of the Wall Street house 
Salomon Bros. said it will scale down the commodities trading operation of its 
Philipp Bros. unit, citing "prolonged difficult market conditions and trading 
losses." A spokeswoman could not provide information on whether the reduction 
would involve job losses or provide other details. 
</P>
</TEXT>
