RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; TELEVISION 
NEWS; NEWS MEDIA; TELEVISION BROADCASTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA081090-0155 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 260064 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 10, 1990, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
