<P>
An emotionally disturbed youth burst into flames when police sprayed him with a 
chemical used like Mace to subdue dangerous people, and the police department 
today suspended use of the chemical. 
</P>
<P>
The spray, known as Captsun, was determined to be flammable after tests 
